It would be nice to have hierarchical issues so that we can easily visualize as well as track issues that relate to a larger "project".  Two examples: 

1. We have a large project that will span multiple versions of our software.  I need to be able to create the different issues related to the different portions of the project and relate them to the larger project issue.  This way I can easily see what issues are left for the project as well as be able to assign different portions of the project to different versions
2. I Have an epic user story that will be implemented in a single version of our software.  I'd like to be able to split the epic user story without having to remove it and replace it with multiple stories. This would allow me to track where we are in the development of the epic user story

